                            </p>
                            
                            <div style="background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #a7f3d0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 17px; color: #1a1a1a;"><t t-out="object.appointment_type_id.name"/></h3>
                                <p style="margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
